1801.text: [1801] RootWebArea 'EleutherAI/gpt-j-6b · Hugging Face' focused: True url: https://huggingface.co/EleutherAI/gpt-j-6b

2703.text: [2703] StaticText '. "GPT-J" refers to the class of model, while "6B" represents the number of trainable parameters.'

3179.text: [3179] StaticText ' Each layer consists of one feedforward block and one self attention block.'

3184.text: [3184] StaticText ' Although the embedding matrix has a size of 50400, only 50257 entries are used by the GPT-2 tokenizer.'

3187.text: [3187] StaticText 'The model consists of 28 layers with a model dimension of 4096, and a feedforward dimension of 16384. The model dimension is split into 16 heads, each with a dimension of 256. Rotary Position Embedding (RoPE) is applied to 64 dimensions of each head. The model is trained with a tokenization vocabulary of 50257, using the same set of BPEs as GPT-2/GPT-3.'

3203.text: [3203] StaticText 'GPT-J learns an inner representation of the English language that can be used to extract features useful for downstream tasks. The model is best at what it was pretrained for however, which is generating text from a prompt.'

3222.text: [3222] StaticText ' intended for deployment without fine-tuning, supervision, and/or moderation. It is not a in itself a product and cannot be used for human-facing interactions. For example, the model may generate harmful or offensive text. Please evaluate the risks associated with your particular use case.'

3225.text: [3225] StaticText 'GPT-J-6B was trained on an English-language only dataset, and is thus '

3228.text: [3228] StaticText ' suitable for translation or generating text in other languages.'

4164.text: [4164] StaticText "This model isn't deployed by any Inference Provider."
